{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 SneakPeak - Waveform Editor for REAPER\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A native C++ extension that provides a precision waveform editor for any media item. Click an item in REAPER and get instant, detailed waveform editing.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Features\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Precision waveform with peak + RMS display and dB scale\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Precision selection and editing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Cut, Copy, Paste, Normalize, Fade, Reverse, Gain\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Real-time spectral analysis with frequency selection\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Multi-item view: Mix, Layered per Item, Layered per Track\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Peak/RMS/VU metering with AES/EBU standard integration\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Minimap, markers, gain knob, solo button\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Standalone WAV editing with drag-and-drop\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Full audio loading for accurate waveform display\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Dockable window, persistent settings\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Zero dependencies - pure C++ extension\sa180\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Dynamics processing: compressor + gate with real-time preview\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Volume envelope editing with freehand drawing\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 Requirements\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab REAPER 7.0+\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab macOS (arm64/x86_64), Windows (x64), Linux (x86_64/aarch64)\sa180\par}
{\pard \qc \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\emdash\par}
